The following components were adapted from this project:
  - CiCode TextMate syntax grammar (syntaxes/cicode.tmLanguage.json)
  - Language configuration (language-configuration.json)
  - IntelliSense providers (completion, hover, signature, navigation, inlay hints)
  - Diagnostics and linting framework
  - Code formatter
  - Code lens (reference counts)
  - CiCode Explorer sidebar
  - Doc skeleton generator
  - Built-in function definitions (builtins/builtinFunctions.json, base data)
  - Extension manifest structure (package.json, contributes schema)

